description: JUICEBOX is the first premium and sustainable juice truck serving the local communities of Los Angeles. JUICEBOX provides healthy, affordable, made-to-order juice using fresh, local, and organic produce on location.To read about JUICEBOX owners Robert Connolly and Robbie Pyle's transition from corporate employees to food truckers pursuing a dream, the eye-opening power of cancer, and why juice is the way to go, check out the Roaming Hunger blog here: http://roaminghunger.com/blog/4944/getting-the-squeeze-on-las-juicebox
name: JUICEBOX
